msgid ""
"<b>An error occurred while updating the signing key.</b>\\n\\n<b>This "
"prevents determining whether an upgrade is available from our website.</"
"b>\\n\\nCheck your network connection and restart Tails.\\n\\nIf the problem "
"persists, try doing a manual upgrade."
msgstr ""
"<b>Tharla earráid agus an eochair shínithe á nuashonrú.</b>\\n\\n<b>Coscann "
"sé seo a chinneadh an bhfuil uasghrádú ar fáil ónár suíomh Gréasáin.</"
"b>\\n\\nSeiceáil do nasc líonra agus atosú Tails.\\n\\nMá leanann an fhadhb, "
"déan iarracht uasghrádú de láimh a dhéanamh."

