"Teastaíonn {memory_needed} de chuimhne in aisce don uasghrádú incriminteach "
"atá ar fáil, ach níl ach {free_memory} ar fáil."

#: config/chroot_local-includes/usr/src/iuk/lib/Tails/IUK/Frontend.pm:473
msgid ""
"An error occurred while detecting available upgrades.\n"
"This should not happen. Please report a bug."
msgstr ""
"Tharla earráid agus uasghráduithe atá ar fáil á mbraith. \n"
"Níor cheart go dtarlódh sé seo. Tuairiscigh fabht le do thoil."

#: config/chroot_local-includes/usr/src/iuk/lib/Tails/IUK/Frontend.pm:476
#: config/chroot_local-includes/usr/src/iuk/lib/Tails/IUK/Frontend.pm:495
msgid "Error while detecting available upgrades"
msgstr "Earráid agus nuashonruithe á lorg"

#: config/chroot_local-includes/usr/src/iuk/lib/Tails/IUK/Frontend.pm:491
msgid ""
"An incremental upgrade is available, but no full upgrade is.\n"
"This should not happen. Please report a bug."
msgstr ""
"Tá nuashonrú incriminteach ar fáil, ach níl aon nuashonrú iomlán ar fáil.\n"
"Tá rud éigin mícheart. Ba chóir duit tuairisc ar an bhfadhb seo a dhéanamh."

#: config/chroot_local-includes/usr/src/iuk/lib/Tails/IUK/Frontend.pm:504
#, perl-brace-format
msgid ""
"<b>You should upgrade to {name} {version}.</b>\n"
"\n"
"For more information about this new version, go to {details_url}\n"
"\n"
"We recommend you close all other applications during the upgrade.\n"
"Downloading the upgrade might take a long time, from several minutes to a "
"few hours.\n"
"\n"
"Download size: {size}\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to upgrade now?"
msgstr ""
"<b>Ba cheart duit {name} {version} a uasghrádú.</b>\n"
"\n"
"Le haghaidh tuilleadh eolais faoin leagan nua seo, téigh go dtí "
