"dhíchumasú ar mhaithe le slándáil mhéadaithe."

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/tails/greeter/additional_settings.ui.in:514
msgid ""
"The Unsafe Browser allows you to sign in to a network using a captive "
"portal.\n"
"\n"
"A captive portal is a web page that is displayed before you can access the "
"Internet. Captive portals usually require you to log in to the network or "
"enter information such as an email address.\n"
"\n"
"The Unsafe Browser is not anonymous and can deanonymize you. Use it only to "
"sign in to networks."
msgstr ""
"Ligeann an Brabhsálaí Neamhshábháilte duit síniú isteach i líonra ag baint "
"úsáide as tairseach gafa.\n"
"\n"
"Is leathanach gréasáin é tairseach gafa a thaispeántar sula bhféadann tú "
"rochtain a fháil ar an Idirlíon. De ghnáth, éilíonn tairseacha gafa ort "
"logáil isteach sa líonra nó faisnéis amhail seoladh ríomhphoist a iontráil.\n"
"\n"
"Níl an Brabhsálaí Neamhshábháilte gan ainm agus is féidir leis tú a dhí-"
"anaithnidiú. Ná húsáid é ach chun síniú isteach i líonraí."

